# TerraLens AI — MVP Upgrade Walkthrough

## Summary

Upgraded TerraLens AI from a hackathon prototype to an MVP-ready platform with **real data**, **corrected indexes**, **expert AI recommendations**, and **proper UI sizing**.

---

## Changes Made

### 1. Real Data Integration

Replaced synthetic data with verified Tunisian sources:

| Data | Source | Verified |
|---|---|---|
| Population (24 gov.) | INS RGPH 2024 Census | Nov 2024 |
| Property prices | Mubawab.tn 2025 reports | Apr 2025 |
| Agencies (80 offices) | tecnocasa.tn, century21.tn, remax.com.tn | Live |
| Unemployment | INS Q3 2024 (16.0% national) | Q3 2024 |
| Risk zones | ANPE/ThinkHazard | Current |

**80 real estate agencies tracked:**
- Tecnocasa: 30 offices
- Century 21: 15 offices  
- RE/MAX: 12 offices
- Independent agencies: 23 offices (Dahmen, El Ikama, Sife, etc.)

